Title: Fuzzy sphere bimodule, ABS construction to the exact soliton solutions
Authors: Bo-yu Hou, Bo-yuan Hou and Rui-hong Yue
Comments: Latex file without figure, 13 pages
\\
  In this paper, we set up the bi-module of the algebra ${\cal A}$ on fuzzy
sphere. Based on the differential operators in moving frame, we generalize the
ABS construction into fuzzy sphere case. The applications of ABS construction
are investigated in various physical systems.
